@ At this point |right_type(q)| is usually |open|, but it may have been
set to some other value by a previous splicing operation. We must maintain
the value of |right_type(q)| in unusual cases such as
`\.{..z1\{z2\}\&\{z3\}z1\{0,0\}..}'.

